xception><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Cite\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Code\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Definition\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Keyboard\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Preformatted\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Sample\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Typewriter\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Variable\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Normal Table\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"annotation subject\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"No List\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Balloon Text\"></w :LsdException></w :LatentStyles></xml><![endif]-->','','','','','','','','','','','','','100','65','0','1414104857');
INSERT INTO `%DB_PREFIX%info` VALUES ('694','29','《关于促进互联网金融健康发展指导意见》近期将出台','','','<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w :WordDocument><w :BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w :BrowserLevel><w :DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w :DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery><w :DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w :DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery><w :DocumentKind>DocumentNotSpecified</w :DocumentKind><w :DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8</w :DrawingGridVerticalSpacing><w :View>Normal</w :View><w :Compatibility><w :DontGrowAutofit/><w :BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/><w :DoNotExpandShiftReturn/><w :UseFELayout/></w :Compatibility><w :Zoom>0</w :Zoom></w :WordDocument></xml><![endif]--><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《关于促进互联网金融健康发展指导意见》（下称《指导意见》）已筹划很久，也是人们期盼已久的P2P行业监管制度。俗话说，“无规矩不成方圆”，在P2P发展浪潮中，有很多跑路平台，使得不少想要投资者，成为了行业的看客。有消息人士透露《指导意见》即将问世，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">对于P2P网贷监管、众筹监管和互联网金融协议监管都有专门的部分负责。在各部门相互监督合作的情况下,互联网金融的发展</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">定会形式大好，从此告别野蛮生长的阶段</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">，必将会给行业带来新的生机。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">近日，据接近央行人士向《第一财经日报》记者透露：“《指导意见</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">》</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">已经上报国务院一段时间了，说不定哪天就公布了。”他称，《指导意见》将比互联网金融协会</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">提早“面世”，随时可能颁布。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 而早前，央行条法司司长穆怀朋已公开表示，央行正在会同有关部门加紧制定《指导意见》，这份《指导意见》作为“顶层设计”，将成为中国互联网金融监管体系的制度基础。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 据上述人士透露，互联网金融的具体分管部门与外界传闻基本相符：央行负责第三方支付和互联网金融协会监管;银监会负责</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\".\">P2P网贷</a>监管;证监会负责众筹的监管。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">P2P网贷行业有关人士则对《第一财经日报》记者表示，7月中旬，央行召集多家互联网金融公司开会，就尚未出台的《指导意见》进行沟通交流，包括其在内的代表性企业都出席了会议。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">根据坊间流传《指导意见》已经完成了政策制定，正等待发布时机。10月20日，广东互联网金融协会会长陈宝国透露，年底之前，央行一定会正式出台《指导意见》。据称，《指导意见》将对两年时间以来互联网金融野蛮生长进行整体上的约束和指引。在部分领域的无序和混乱局面将得到改善，互联网金融将回归到合&nbsp;理规范的轨道之上。</span></p>\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w :LatentStyles deflockedstate=\"false\" defunhidewhenused=\"true\" defsemihidden=\"true\" defqformat=\"false\" defpriority=\"99\" latentstylecount=\"156\"><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Normal\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 1\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 2\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 3\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 4\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 5\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 6\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 7\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 8\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 9\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 1\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 2\"></w :LsdException><w