/w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Variable\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Normal Table\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"annotation subject\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"No List\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Balloon Text\"></w :LsdException></w :LatentStyles></xml><![endif]-->','','','','','','','','','','','','','100','64','0','1414105041');
INSERT INTO `%DB_PREFIX%info` VALUES ('695','29','理财秘籍：钱少更要“理”，低收入如何理财','','','<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w :WordDocument><w :BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w :BrowserLevel><w :DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w :DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery><w :DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w :DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery><w :DocumentKind>DocumentNotSpecified</w :DocumentKind><w :DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8</w :DrawingGridVerticalSpacing><w :View>Normal</w :View><w :Compatibility><w :DontGrowAutofit/><w :BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/><w :DoNotExpandShiftReturn/><w :UseFELayout/></w :Compatibility><w :Zoom>0</w :Zoom></w :WordDocument></xml><![endif]--><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不少人因为钱少且收入低，觉得自己没有钱来理财，其实越是这样，越要重视理财，如此方能成为有钱人。不过对钱少收入低的人群来说，在理财的时候，需要更加谨慎，毕竟其抗风险能力较低。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><b>建议一：</b>积极攒钱。“收入少，消费却不少……”这是目前大多数低收入家庭所面临的问题。要获取家庭的“第一桶金”，首先要减少固定开支，即通过减少家庭的即期消费来积累剩余，再用这些剩余资产进行投资。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b>建议二：</b>善买保险。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">我认为医疗保险是需要买的，不过大多数单位都会交。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">重病住院，动辄就是几万元乃至十几万元。一场大病，就可以让家庭倾家荡产甚至负债累累。因此，低收入家庭在理财时更需要</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">确保每人都有医疗保险</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">来提高家庭风险防范能力，转移风险，从而达到摆脱困境的目的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b>建议三：</b>慎重<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"./\">投资</a>。对于低收入家庭来说，薪水往往较低，经不住大亏，因此，在投资之前要有心理准备，首先要了解投资与回报的评估，也就是投资回报率。要基本了解不同投资方式的运作，所有的投资方式都会有风险，只不过是大小而已，但对于低收入家庭来说，安全性应该是最重要的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b> 建议四：</b></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"./\">P2P理财</a>定投，巧选高收益，但要安全的理财产品。P2P理财一方面门槛低，高回报，另一方面属于短期投资，方便资金周转，适合低收入家庭。比如，金湧博发的P2P理财产品，年化收益14%，两万元起投。门槛低，收益高，非常适合低收入家庭。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">钱少，不是问题！问题在于钱少人懒。所以，财富增长，需要勤于理财。</span></p>\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w :LatentStyles deflockedstate=\"false\" defunhidewhenused=\"true\" defsemihidden=\"true\" defqformat=\"false\" defpriority=\"99\" latentstylecount=\"156\"><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Normal\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 1\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 2\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 3\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 4\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 5\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 6\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 7\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 8\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 9\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 1\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 2\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 3\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 4\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 5\"></w :LsdEx