TML Typewriter\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"HTML Variable\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Normal Table\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"annotation subject\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"No List\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Balloon Text\"></w :LsdException></w :LatentStyles></xml><![endif]-->','','','','','','','','','','','','','100','72','0','1414540353');
INSERT INTO `%DB_PREFIX%info` VALUES ('705','29','金湧博发理财师教你做个明白的投资人','','','<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w :WordDocument><w :BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w :BrowserLevel><w :DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w :DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery><w :DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w :DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery><w :DocumentKind>DocumentNotSpecified</w :DocumentKind><w :DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8</w :DrawingGridVerticalSpacing><w :View>Normal</w :View><w :Compatibility><w :DontGrowAutofit/><w :BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/><w :DoNotExpandShiftReturn/><w :UseFELayout/></w :Compatibility><w :Zoom>0</w :Zoom></w :WordDocument></xml><![endif]--><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 理财时代来了，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">想实现财富稳定增值的投资者不在少数，现在互联网理财网站很多，懒人理财工具也不少，很多投资人觉得选择了理财工具就可高枕无忧了。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">金湧博发理财师</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">在这里提醒大家，在保证稳定收益的情况下，做好个人理财</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">，让自己的收益最大化。投资理财要掌握好产品特性，了解行业发展，做个明白的投资人。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">　</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 没有理财万能工具</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;投资人切勿偷懒</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">　　</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 现今，有很多投资者总想着寻找一些简单的投资工具，最好是万能的，无需费时费力，在家坐等赚钱，但这可能实现吗?这句“理财有风险，投资需谨慎”的话，忘记了吗?一般而言，理财工具有三大属性：收益性、风险性和流动性，而很少有一种理财工具在这三方面都能完胜的。就比如定存，钱存银行基本没风险，但是利息低，5年4.25%。可以参考一些<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"./\">P2P固定收益类理财</a></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">产品，风险相对来说也较低，有些平台还可以进行债权转让</span><span><a href=\"http://www.eloancn.com/new/loadAllPublishingCreditAssignList.action\"></a></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">，当然如果手中这笔资金暂时无他用，选择此投资还不错。所以，别指望有任何万能理财工具，几乎不“存在”，而要根据你的理财需求，风险偏好等选择最适合你的理财工具才是上策。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">　　</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">投资人切勿</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">过度投资&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">　　</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 理财，能帮助合理分配资产，实现财富增值。但是若过度投资或过度关注，就会让理财转变为投机。经常见到这样的投资者，因期望过高收益，便投入更多资金，期望能投入越多，收益越高，这就好比“慢性自杀”，一旦投资失败，本金“随之东流”。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">金湧博发</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">理财师提醒投资者，理财是一个循序渐进的过程，资金应合理安排，哪些资金用于日常开销，哪些资金用于低风险投资，哪些资金可以用来投资高风险高收益产品，都应该事先做好规划。不要对投资能赚很多钱有过高的期望，避免过&nbsp;度投资。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">时刻关注自己的投资</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">　&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 经常会有这样一些投资者，在某个<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"./\">互联网金融</a></span><span><a href=\"http://www.eloancn.com/news-1649.html\"></a></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">网认购了理财产品后，就“了无音信”，甚至产品到期了都不知道。对于这样的投资者，理财师只能说：对自己的钱太不“负责”了。要知道投资不关注，等于“不投&nbsp;资”。投资者在进行了某项投资后，还需时刻关注项目后期的运营情况，市场行情等，能时时调整投资策略，将投资风险降到最低，才能实现收益最大化。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent:24.5000pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent:24.5000pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">你有多懒，你的投资就有多险，既然选择投资，就要追求最高效益。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">别指望靠几个简单投资工具就能赚钱，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">一定要学会观察、规划，做个明白的投资人，自己成为掌舵人。</span></p>\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w :LatentStyles deflockedstate=\"false\" defunhidewhenused=\"true\" defsemihidden=\"true\" defqformat=\"false\" defpriority=\"99\" latentstylecount=\"156\"><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"Normal\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 1\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 2\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 3\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 4\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 5\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 6\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 7\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 8\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"heading 9\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 1\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 2\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 3\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 4\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 5\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 6\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 7\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 8\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"index 9\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"toc 1\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"toc 2\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\"false\" priority=\"99\" name=\"toc 3\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked